<h3>Kid Passions</h3>
<p>This SVG animation titled "Kid Passions" had one goal in mind; subtle and simplistic. It was essential that each orb circling the child float delicately and randomly emit waves precisely to the brain resulting in separate signal transmitted through the child's body. The final touches would be eye movement and breathing to further portray a sense of realism.</p>
