<h3>Underneath</h3>
<p>Using the following illustration titled "Underneath" by <a href="http://www.isaiahsaxon.com">Isaiah Saxon</a>, it was requested to create an animation sequence that was subtle and sparked curiousity. What makes this animation entertaining are the tiny and intricate pieces to discover; the arm bend, worm crawl, bug movements, rock lift, foot wiggle and even the fireflies within the jar.</p>
